Extra Text: Oh my there vegan pizza is so good. My boyfriend has a dairy allergy so we can’t eat out much. We get scared to order but when I found this place and the server acknowledged they have options for him. We got super happy. Food was delicious and we will be back: thank you!
interesting and delicious food.  maitress d' and wait staff welcoming and helpful.
great food and ambience. Service was efficient and quick and very friendly.
It was perfect. Great menu and staff. Everything was wonderful
When food in the city has become so expensive and so hype-y, I can always count on Westville for an amazing meal with great service.
Overall an excellent experience! I would def reccomend to people and would absolutely go back. Food was fantastic!
Excellent Business Lunch! Food was amazing! Tuna Nachos are my fav!
The food was delicious.  And the cappuccinos are amazing.  Would totally recommend.
Food is great except their signature. Great drink. Very loud inside the restaurant. Nice decoration.
Avery was AMAZING!! We had a great time at brunch!! Food was incredible and so were the drinks!
Really cool restaurant, cool ambiance, food is good.

The food is really really good in a sea of mediocre Mexican food out there. The menu is limited, but the choices are good and sufficient. This is a small and tightly packed restaurant/bar, and therefore noisy, but in a friendly and festive way. The servers were courteous and attentive and food was delivered to the table quickly. Drinks very good. A nice find!
Cozy setting with fantastic service and delicious food. Ramen was excellent.

I arrived on time but my date was a little late. Host was absolutely awesome. Waited at the bar. Host got us a great table when we were ready. Fully packed. Service was fantastic, Food came out so fast I thought they knew what the order was before I ordered it! Overall a very nice experience, highly recommend!
Great food and great service. Went for restaurant week and ordered the meatballs and hanger steak - both were exceptional!
Love it! Great food and ambiance and prices , love the poke bowl
Excellent food and service. Ambiance a bit dated but overall a great experience.

Restaurant name: The Dining Room at RH Guesthouse New York
Extra Text: Incredible all around can’t say enough good things

love treadwell — great casual option + always happy with quality of the food. plethora of bar games available alongside tvs in every direction. grab a cold one with friends + family and enjoy all around
Amazing food, drinks, and desert! Will definitely return!
This restaurant is a hidden gem. The food was wonderful and the service was flawlessly executed. I am so looking forward to dining there again!!

Restaurant name: T. Brasserie at Tin Building by Jean-Georges
Extra Text: Fantastic value for restaurant week, no skimping on portions or quality like many other places. Food was great and the service outstanding. I will definitely be back.
That was hands down the best experience and ramen i’ve ever had
Food was fantastic. Love the vibe of a restaurant and the staff are top notch!
The sommelier we had was absolutely incredible and took the time to teach us about the wine we were drinking. We had such a wonderful time!
The food and service is without compare!! It was crazy busy so we forgive that they forgot our birthday.
Bistro Les Ami provided us with a delicious lunch of beautifully prepared French food. My steaks frites and my husband's chicken paillard both were wonderful.
Amazing.  Frank did not disappoint.  Great hospitality.  A must stop if you’re in the neighborhood.
The service, the food and everything was AMAZING!!! They went above and beyond!!! Will def be coming back soon!!!
